OL,4,CChinese-owned Volvo takes on Sweden's
OL,5,Cfamily values
OL,6, Swedish carmaker Volvo will offer a
OL,7, generous paid parental leave scheme to
OL,8, its 40,000 employees globally.
OL,10,FParental leave benefit is often
OL,11,Fgenerous at Swedish companies, and now
OL,12,FVolvo's scheme will apply to all of its
OL,13,Femployees, including China and the US.
OL,15,FUnder the plan, staff will be entitled
OL,16,Fto 24 weeks of paid parental leave
OL,17,Fwhile receiving 80% of their base pay
OL,18,Fduring the leave period.
OL,20,FHeadquartered in Sweden, Volvo is owned
OL,21,Fby China's biggest carmaker Geely.
